350
00:13:52,637 --> 00:13:53,713
Dạ đúng thật ạ.

351
00:13:53,717 --> 00:13:54,721
Shin thì...

352
00:13:54,725 --> 00:13:55,681
Heheh

353
00:13:55,991 --> 00:13:56,987
Shin thì...

354
00:13:57,882 --> 00:13:59,513
