388
00:15:12,418 --> 00:15:13,309
Chúng ta cùng mời ông ấy ra nhé?

389
00:15:13,313 --> 00:15:14,321
Mời ông ra sân khấu!

390
00:15:17,087 --> 00:15:17,917
Chà.

391
00:15:18,529 --> 00:15:19,803
Hah...

392
00:15:19,807 --> 00:15:20,542
Heh...

