396
00:15:24,941 --> 00:15:25,690
Ừm.

397
00:15:26,143 --> 00:15:27,930
Um.... Ta 98 tuổi rồi.

398
00:15:28,677 --> 00:15:29,808
Ta là thiên tài

399
00:15:29,812 --> 00:15:31,070
meme.

400
00:15:31,074 --> 00:15:32,103
No Gang-ja.

401
00:15:32,107 --> 00:15:34,575
